@{bg shine}PC HURTS@{bg back}


And it hurts, and it hurts, and it hurts,         @{fg shine}@{bg text}-----------------@{fg text}@{bg back}
                                PC hurts.         @{fg shine}@{bg text}|p  c    u s e r|@{fg text}@{bg back}
                                                  @{fg shine}@{bg text}-----------------@{fg text}@{bg back}
And it hurts, and it hurts, and it hurts,         @{fg shine}@{bg text}|@{fg text}@{bg shine}A D V I S O R Y@{fg shine}@{bg text}|@{fg text}@{bg back}
                                PC hurts.         @{fg shine}@{bg text}-----------------@{fg text}@{bg back}
                                                  @{fg shine}@{bg text}|explicit lyrics|@{fg text}@{bg back}
                                                  @{fg shine}@{bg text}-----------------@{fg text}@{bg back}
PC stops the imagination in my mind,

makes me mad when it crashes many times.

Why didn't I keep my Intel Outside,

don't you know how hard I cried.


PC hurts, PC hurts, when it works.

PC hurts, when it works, PC hurts.

PC hurts, PC hurts, when it works.

PC hurts, when it works, PC hurts.

@{b}There will be a day when PC dies;

there will be a day when PC dies.@{ub}



And it hurts, and it hurts, and it hurts,
                                PC hurts.

And it hurts, and it hurts, and it hurts,
                                PC hurts.



It would be better to look to the future,

but it's not, really not, the Bill's one.

Amiga's lymph still flows in our hearts,

this great sensation with PC doesn't come.


PC hurts, PC hurts, when it works.

PC hurts, when it works, PC hurts.

PC hurts, PC hurts, when it works.

PC hurts, when it works, PC hurts.@{b}

There will be a day when PC dies;

there will be a day when PC dies.@{ub}


Yes...

The day will come.

The day when Bill will beg at the entrance of World Of Amiga,

and Peter will clean up shoes to the visitors.

- @{i}Crazy laughes@{ui}  8) -
@endnode

