                               @{b}DISTRIBUTION@{ub}
                               @{fg shine}~~~~~~~~~~~~@{fg text}

 Any commercial use of this material is ILLEGAL, however files contained
 in this archive can be copied freely without any fee (support cost only),
 but take care: this archive can be placed only on Aminet, on "Amiga
 based" CD-ROMs, floppy disks and BBSs.

 The files contained in the archive PC_Hurts.lha
 -----------------------------------------------
 PC_Hurts.med            Music module (MED MMD1)
 PC_Hurts_Cover.ilbm     Pseudo-cover of the track
 PC_Hurts.guide          This AmigaGuide file
 PC_Hurts.ReadMe         A short ReadMe text file
 Bonus_Samples.lha       Some noises during voice recording... ;)
 #?.info                 Icons (as you know :)

 Note: the pseudo-cover is 736x566x8 (video overscan 256 colors).
@endnode

